   "body" : "Seen while reviewing/testing #13084 and #17204 that both needed a regression test.\r\n\r\nThis PR applies the `OP_RIGHT` script opcode defined in `src/script/script.h:119` to the `OP_1NEGATE` check in `src/script/interpreter.cpp`, and adds a regression test based on https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/13084#issuecomment-384795684 to ensure `OP_1NEGATE` satisfies the BIP62 minimal push standardness rule. The test fails at the commit immediately before each of these PRs and passes with their fixes. It also passes on current master; the issue appears to have been fixed in the interim.\r\n\r\nCloses #17204.",
